      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Nocturnal Tracker",
        "Client": "Wandering Bard",
        "Description": "The Plains at night are quite\r\nelegant and inspiring... But\r\nsomeone or someTHING is\r\nfollowing me. I feel so afraid\r\nthat all my ideas and emotions\r\nare simply swept away!\r\nPlease get rid of this stalker!",
        "Target": "Hunt an Anjanath",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Traqueur nocturne",
        "Client": "Po\u00E8te errant",
        "Description": "De nuit, les Plaines de sable\r\nm\u0027inspirent beaucoup... Mais\r\nil y a quelque chose ou\r\nquelqu\u0027un qui me suit. La peur\r\nbloque mon inspiration, je\r\nn\u0027arrive plus \u00E0 \u00E9crire !\r\nAide-moi, je t\u0027en prie !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Anjanath",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Segugio notturno",
        "Client": "Poeta girovago",
        "Description": "Le Piane sabbiose di notte\r\nsono stupende e stimolanti...\r\nMa qualcuno o qualcosa mi sta\r\nseguendo. Sono cos\u00EC spaventato\r\nche tutte le mie emozioni e\r\nle mie idee sono svanite.\r\nTi prego, caccia quel coso!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Anjanath",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "N\u00E4chtlicher Verfolger",
        "Client": "Wandernder Barde",
        "Description": "Die Sandebene bei Nacht ist\r\nso inspirierend... Aber jemand\r\n\u2013 oder ETWAS \u2013 verfolgt mich.\r\nVor Angst kann ich nicht mehr\r\nklar denken und alle Ideen\r\nentgleiten mir. Bitte schalte\r\nmeinen Verfolger aus!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Anjanath.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Rastreador nocturno",
        "Client": "Poeta errante",
        "Description": "Los Llanos arenosos son muy\r\nelegantes e inspiradores por\r\nla noche... Pero alguien o\r\nalgo me acecha. \u00A1Me da tanto\r\nmiedo que todas mis ideas y\r\nemociones se desvanecen!\r\nPor favor, caza esa... \u00A1cosa!",
