      {
        "Language": "POL",
        "Name": "Nocny tropiciel",
        "Client": "Podr\u00F3\u017Cny bard",
        "Description": "Noc\u0105 R\u00F3wniny s\u0105 bardzo\r\neleganckie i inspiruj\u0105ce...\r\nAle kto\u015B lub CO\u015A mnie \u015Bledzi.\r\nTak si\u0119 boj\u0119, \u017Ce wszystkie\r\nmoje pomys\u0142y i emocje\r\ns\u0105 st\u0142umione! Prosz\u0119, upoluj\r\ntego prze\u015Bladowc\u0119!",
        "Target": "Upoluj Anjanatha",
        "Fail": "Nagroda = 0 lub koniec czasu"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POR",
        "Name": "Rastreador noturno",
        "Client": "Bardo andarilho",
        "Description": "\u00C0 noite, a Plan\u00EDcie Arenosa \u00E9\r\num po\u00E7o de eleg\u00E2ncia e\r\ninspira\u00E7\u00E3o! Mas algu\u00E9m, ou\r\nalgo, t\u00E1 me seguindo. T\u00F4 com\r\ntanto medo de roubarem minhas\r\nideias e emo\u00E7\u00F5es! Por favor,\r\nlivre-se daquela coisa!",
